correctness.rationale: The extraction contains many fabricated values, schema violations, and mismatches with the article. Key issues: (1) Reactant selection: coReactant lists only H2O, but the article states H2O and O3 were used as oxygen sources; carrierGas and purgingGas are set to 'Not Found' (not traceable and unacceptable for required fields). (2) Process parameters: temperature 200 °C is not reported; pressure 0.6 Pa is the sputtering pressure (not ALD) and uses an invalid unit per schema (expects MilliM_HG); substrate 'thermally grown SiO2/Si' is not stated in the paper; reactor manufacturer is given in the paper (Shanghai Atomic Semiconductor Co.,Ltd.) but marked 'Not Found'; plasmaPower is set to None (wrong type for an object field and not applicable for TALD); numerous dosing/purging/flow values are invented and use wrong units (SEC instead of MilliSEC; GPC in NanoM instead of ANGSTROM); saturation and nucleationPeriod are unreported; filmThickness is duplicated both inside thicknessControl and again at the same level (violates additionalProperties: false). (3) SupercycleDesign: counts 5/3/4 and sequence In2O3→Ga2O3→ZnO are correct. (4) Material properties: refractiveIndex, absorptionCoefficient, resistivity, carrierDensity, uniformity, conformality, composition (33.33% and 1:1:1), crystallinity by XRD, roughness by AFM are not reported in the paper; absorptionCoefficient uses an invalid unit per schema; filmDensity 5.60 g/cm3 is mentioned, but method XRR is not stated. (5) Electrical/device data: field-effect mobility 36.2 cm2/Vs, Vth 0.05 V, SS 82 mV/dec match the BI device; however onOffRatio is incorrectly 1e10 (table shows 1e9); electricalProperties.mobility is labeled as Hall measurements (no Hall data in the article and 36.2 cm2/Vs is from TFT FE mobility). (6) Schema compliance: multiple unit mismatches (pressure, dosing/purging times, GPC), invalid None type, and extra filmThickness field. Corrections needed: include O3 in coReactant; replace 'Not Found' entries with article-backed values or omit optional fields; fix units to schema enumerations; remove fabricated dosing/purge/flow/GPC/uniformity/conformality/composition/XRD/AFM/Hall entries; correct onOffRatio to 1e9; set reactor.manufacturer to Shanghai Atomic Semiconductor Co.,Ltd.; ensure pressure corresponds to ALD (or omit if unknown) and uses MilliM_HG.

completeness.rationale: Extraction is largely incomplete and incorrect relative to the article and the schema. Major issues: (1) Missing processes: the paper reports two distinct IGZO ALD depositions (30 nm IGZO via TH‑ALD for SI‑A and 10 nm IGZO via TH‑ALD as the front layer in BI). Only one process (10 nm) is extracted; the SI‑A ALD process is absent. (2) Unsupported or wrong parameters: ALD temperature (set to 200 °C) not reported; ALD pressure (0.6 Pa) is from sputtering, not ALD; substrate listed as “thermally grown SiO2/Si” is not stated; reactor manufacturer (“Shanghai Atomic Semiconductor Co.,Ltd.”) is given in the article but marked “Not Found.” (3) Reactants: Article states H2O and O3 as oxygen sources; extraction lists only H2O for all sub‑cycles, omitting O3. Carrier/purging gases are unknown in the paper but filled with placeholders (“Not Found”), violating the no-placeholder requirement. (4) Many invented values with no traceability: GPC, number of cycles, saturation, nucleation period, dosing/purge times, flow rates, uniformity, conformality, roughness, composition (33.33% and 1:1:1), resistivity, carrier density, and “Hall measurements” are not reported. (5) Schema violations/units: plasmaPower set to null (wrong type), pressure unit uses Pa instead of required MilliM_HG, dosing/purge times use SEC instead of MilliSEC, filmDensity unit GM-PER-DeciM3 with 5.6 contradicts 5.60 g cm^-3 in text, absorptionCoefficient unit not allowed by schema. (6) Device metrics: on/off ratio extracted as 1e10, but BI is 1e9 per Table 1; mobility, Vth, and SS are correct. (7) Supercycle design is correctly captured (5:3:4 and sequence), but overall the process is not coherent due to numerous unsupported values. Needed corrections: add a separate SI‑A ALD process; fix co‑reactants to include O3; fill reactor manufacturer; remove/replace all invented parameters with only traceable values; correct units to schema (e.g., MilliSEC, MilliM_HG); correct on/off ratio to 1e9; correct film density units or omit if not measured; avoid null/placeholder fields.
